<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id37046602-2930-11f1-b70e-e9fd6f164ed0" identifier="/us/usc/t3/s8"><num value="8">§ 8.</num><heading> Manner of voting</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The electors shall vote for President and Vice President, respectively, in the manner directed by the Constitution.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id37046603-2930-11f1-b70e-e9fd6f164ed0">(<ref href="/us/act/1948-06-25/ch644">June 25, 1948, ch. 644</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/62/674">62 Stat. 674</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
